$Id$

- The gaim_conversation_get/set_data() routines
  provide storage for the fields needed for encryption
  Any such field is prefixed with `/grypt/'.

  These fields include:

+-----------------------+---------------+-----------------------+
| Underlying Type	| Field Name	| Description		|
+-----------------------+---------------+-----------------------+
| int *			| state		| Session crypto state	|
| gpgme_recipients_t	| key		| GPGME recipient	|
+-----------------------+---------------+-----------------------+
